54:23.302 --> 54:26.920
But you must put those sentiments
to one side now,

54:27.014 --> 54:29.141
for duty calls.

54:29.892 --> 54:33.635
The grief for your father’s death
will be felt far and wide.

54:34.147 --> 54:37.264
Your people will need
your strength and leadership.

54:37.525 --> 54:39.857
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

